title: Mets reach NLCS after beating Dodgers in Game 5
text:
Baseball The New York Mets' Daniel Murphy, right, celebrates with Yoenis Cespedes, left, after hitting a home run during the sixth inning in Game 5 of baseball's National League Division Series against the Los Angeles Dodgers Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Los Angeles. The Mets won 3-2. (Lenny Ignelzi/AP) The New York Mets' Daniel Murphy, right, celebrates with Yoenis Cespedes, left, after hitting a home run during the sixth inning in Game 5 of baseball's National League Division Series against the Los Angeles Dodgers Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in Los Angeles.
